Fixed the ValueError: If using all scalar values, you must pass an index by ensuring that coef, se, z, p, and or_val are treated as pandas Series (which have an index) rather than scalars. Added a helper function get_series_or_nan to safely extract the column as a pandas Series, or return a Series of NaNs with the correct index if the attribute is missing or None.

